sentences.english: This jadeite is Bean Green variety.
It of the whole body, like a piece of green jade .

sentences.english: The streets are paved with jade there my brother always said.

sentences.english: We make some pretty good emerald-jade beef croquettes.

sentences.english: As usual, a pair of White-Breasted Kingfishers nest near my home this summer.

sentences.english: Hainan Island was called the Pearl Cliffs, Fine Jade Cliffs, and the Fine Jade Land.

sentences.english: On the newspaper session, seven jadeite kings still announced tomorrow's game rule.

sentences.english: Some green leaves transparent, like Jade, a lovely and tender.
